stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> ABSENT
  ABSENT --> LOADING: cache miss
  LOADING --> READY: load from store
  READY --> PINNED: optimizer acquires snapshot
  PINNED --> READY: optimizer releases
  READY --> REPLACED: ANALYZE publishes new snapshot
  PINNED --> REPLACED: new snapshot published while old is in use
  REPLACED --> EVICTED: no pins remain
  READY --> STALE: DDL changes dictionary version
  PINNED --> STALE: DDL marks version stale
  STALE --> EVICTED: no pins remain
  EVICTED --> [*]
